<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/newPorfolio.css">
    <style>
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            padding: 20px 0;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer div {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            color: #ccc;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('nav.ejs') %>
        <section style="display: flex; align-items: center; height: 100vh; padding: 0 5%;">
            <div style="display: flex; flex: 1; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <div style="flex: 2; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;">
                    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5em; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                        Hi, my name is <br>
                        <span style="color: #ff4b4b; font-size: 3em;">Rehaman</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p style="font-size: 1.25em; line-height: 1.5; color: #555;">
                        I'm a <span style="color: #ff4b4b; font-size: 1.5em;">Full-Stack Developer</span> with a passion
                        for
                        building web applications and solving complex problems.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div style="flex: 1; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
                    <div style="height: 60%; width: auto;">
                        <img style="height: 100%; width: auto; border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);"
                            src="/assets/images/newPortfolio/cartoon_guy.jpeg" alt="Rehaman">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <hr>
        <section style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; padding: 50px 0;">
            <div style="max-width: 800px; text-align: left;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 2em; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #333;">About Me</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 1.25em; line-height: 1.6; color: #555;">
                    I’m Rehaman, a Full-Stack Developer with a deep passion for crafting dynamic and user-friendly web
                    applications.
                    With experience in both front-end and back-end technologies, I enjoy building solutions that are not
                    only functional but
                    also provide a seamless user experience.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.25em; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; margin-top: 20px;">
                    Over the years, I’ve honed my skills in various programming languages, frameworks, and tools.
                    Whether
                    it's developing robust APIs,
                    designing intuitive interfaces, or optimizing performance, I thrive on the challenges that come with
                    turning ideas into reality.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <hr>
        <section style="padding: 50px 0; background-color: #f9f9f9;">
            <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 2.5em; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #333;">Projects</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 1.25em; line-height: 1.6; color: #555;">
                    Here are a few examples of the projects I’ve worked on, including full-stack development and game
                    development.
                </p>
                <a href="/portfolio/projects"
                    style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 30px; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 1.2em; color: #fff; background-color: #ff4b4b; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">
                    View All Projects
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
        <%- include('footer.ejs') %>



</body>

</html>